# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PageForge AI — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# THIS APP RUNS WITH ZERO API KEYS.
#
# The only optional variable is SESSION_SECRET, used to sign user
# session cookies. If not provided, a random one is generated on
# first run and saved to data/.session-secret.
#
# To override, copy this file to .env.local and set your own value.
#
# Generate a strong secret with:
#   node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# SESSION_SECRET=your-64-character-hex-string-here

# Optional: set to "production" when deploying
# NODE_ENV=development
